</div><div class="supplementary-material"><a name="pone.0228632.s007" id="pone.0228632.s007" class="link-target"></a><h3 class="siTitle title-small"><a href="article/file?type=supplementary&amp;id=10.1371/journal.pone.0228632.s007">S1 Appendix. </a>Cohort definitions.</h3><p class="siDoi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0228632.s007">https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0228632.s007</a></p><a id="article1.body1.sec5.supplementary-material7.caption1.p1" name="article1.body1.sec5.supplementary-material7.caption1.p1" class="link-target"></a><p class="postSiDOI">(DOCX)</p>
